## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not cover all aspects of the impact of embedded computers and IoT. The information is also subject to the publication dates of the sources, which may not reflect the most current technological advancements or security developments. Additionally, the perspectives provided are limited to the authors of the cited sources and may not encompass all user experiences or potential future applications.